## OMNI

- Back-end: Node.js
- DataBase:
  - (Docker)PostgreSQL-> User, Account, Relationships, Permissions...
  - MongoDB    -> Messages, History...
  - Redis            -> Socket.io, Sessions, Rooms...
- Frame: React.js/Next.js
- Sessions:Socket.io/WebSockets
- Media:WebAssembly (Wasm) + FFmpeg.wasm
- Game(Embed): Pixi.js

